    "description": "Ball.com microservices — REST-endpoints per service plus een demo-scenario dat eventual consistency laat zien.\n\nServices die HTTP aanbieden:\n- order (write): http://localhost:5000\n- order-read: http://localhost:5010\n- payment: http://localhost:5001\n- catalog: http://localhost:5002\n- customer: http://localhost:5003\n- shipping: http://localhost:5004\n- warehouse: http://localhost:5100\n\nStart eerst de stack met `docker compose up --build`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "49384083"
  },
